CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 9, 1959, pg. A16, reads: "Chic - A pair of stunning Pittsburgh models, not seen too often lately, are Dorothy McCullom and Ethel Littlejohn.  At the Beauty Shop Owners' show, they were standouts."
TitMainTitle: Dorothy McCollum and Ethel Littlejohn posed before wire arches at Beauty Shop Owners' fashion show, Roosevelt Hotel
